            "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\"><strong>Archetype</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.archetypes.XZwGLLgC1sIKlR1c]{Staff Acrobat}<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong> Staff Acrobat Dedication<br><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding your staff.<br></span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>You @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.d5I6018Mci2SWokk]{Leap} and then Strike using your staff. You gain a circumstance bonus to damage for the Strike equal to twice the number of weapon damage dice. Regardless of whether your Strike hit, you can then attempt to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.7blmbDrQFNfdT731]{Shove} or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.ge56Lu1xXVFYUnLP]{Trip} the target.&nbsp;</p>",
